name: A Tiny Alien Choir
description:
A musical, interactive 3D Objkt.

"While on a midnight walk, I felt a small sting on my finger. Expecting some kind of wound, I inspected my thumb— yet what rested on my finger was no wound. What rested on my finger were five strange beings that resembled.... A Tiny Alien Choir?"

Best with headphones or nice speakers :)
